<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Hydrological processes primarily influence this alliance. Fires that do occur spread largely from adjacent burning vegetation. Stems and trunks are easily top-killed by fire, but plants sprout from basal buds.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
			<td class="key">Fire return interval</td>
